name: Printable Sesame Street Elmo Custom Photo Birthday Invitation Design
description:
This is a personalized Sesame Street digital photo birthday invitation. Your invitation will be customized with all your information and e-mailed to you so that you can have them printed at the photo-lab of your choice. You can also email them as e-vites if you prefer! Almost anything on the design can be customized, including the fonts, colors & wording. Any design can be done with or without a photo! Your choice of size -- 4x6 or 5x7.

Also Available:
~ matching thank you design
~ matching address labels
~ matching candy bar wrappers
~ matching water/bubble/soda bottle wrappers
~ matching stickers
~ matching cupcake toppers
~ matching treat bag tags


HOW IT WORKS:

1. Purchase the design of your choice, or contact me to request a custom design. After paying via Paypal, send me an email at pixelboutique@aol.com and include your photo and all of your party info (Name, age, date, time, address, RSVP info, etc.) Be sure to also let me know which size you would like -- 4x6 or 5x7!

2. I will email you a proof within 48 hours (but usually much sooner) of recieving all your information. At that time, you can request any changes that you would like to be made. Once I receive your final approval, I will email you your final high-resolution file. After that, all you need to do is take the file or upload it to your favorite photo-lab and have it printed! Its as simple as that!!!

name: DIY Custom Jones Soda Bottle Wrappers PDF - The Perfect Party Favor
description:
This is a completely customizable bottle wrapper, designed to look like the labels of those ever so popluar (and yummy) brand name sodas! I will add 2 photos of your choosing and whatever wording you would like to the design. The colors can also be changed to match your soda flavor or party colors. Completely customizable... the skys the limit!

These make the most adorable party favors -- perfect for birthdays, weddings, engagement parties, rehersal dinners, anniversaries, BBQs... anything that you want to celebrate!

This listing is for a PDF file that you can print yourself. This way you can print as many or as few as you need. 

PLEASE NOTE: These labels are not waterproof unless you print them on waterproof paper. You can attach them to your bottles using double stick tape, regular tape or a glue stick.

HOW IT WORKS:

1. Purchase this listing and pay via Paypal. After completing the payment process, send me an email at pixelboutique@aol.com and include the following:

~ Two photos (one for the front and one for the back)... please indicate if you would like the photos to be in color or black & white

~ the wording that you would like on the front & side of the label design

~ your info for the NUTRITION FACTS and INGREDIENTS sections

~ the color you would like the colored text to be

~ any other special requests you may have

2. I will email you a proof within 48 hours (but usually much sooner) of receiving all your information. At that time, you can request any changes that you would like to be made. Once I receive your final approval, I will email you your final high-resolution file that you can print yourself at home.
